{"word":"Arrow","slug":"arrow","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Arrow</b> A weapon.<br/> Used in hunting<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=20'>Gen 21:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=3'>Gen 27:3</a><br/> Used in war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=3'>1Sa 31:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=15'>2Sa 22:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=34'>1Ki 22:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19&verse=32'>2Ki 19:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=7&verse=13'>Psa 7:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=22&verse=3'>Isa 22:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=3'>Jer 51:3</a><br/> Divination by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=21&verse=21'>Eze 21:21</a><br/> Shot by Jonathan as a sign to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=20&verse=42'>1Sa 20:42</a><br/> Shot by Joash as a sign against the Syrians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=19'>2Ki 13:19</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=24&verse=8'>Num 24:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=23'>Deu 32:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=42'>Deu 32:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=6&verse=4'>Job 6:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=11&verse=2'>Psa 11:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=21&verse=12'>Psa 21:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=38&verse=2'>Psa 38:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=45&verse=5'>Psa 45:5</a>; <a href